# TransformResolveSystem (SandboxApp)

## Purpose
App tier of transform resolution. Aggregates every SandboxApp transform change request (one request
type per app mover, since the one-adder rule forbids two systems adding the same type) into the single
engine-typed ResolvedTransformRequestOneFrameComponent that the engine TransformResolveSystem applies.
For each requested entity it merges the set channels of all present app requests (later mover wins per
channel) and emits one resolved request. Sole adder of ResolvedTransformRequestOneFrameComponent.

## Input Components
| Component | Access |
|---|---|
| SceneTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | read |
| QuadSpawnTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | read |
| AnimationTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | read |
| CharacterTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | read |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResolvedTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | add (oneframe) | one aggregated request per requested entity |
